the app works for an Inspiron 6400.
I had trouble with the syntax for the HDD password.
Basically, if your tag is ABCDEFG-595B the syntax on the screen should look like this for bios password reset: 
Input #ABCDEFG-595B *
For the hard drive it needs 11 characters but my drive only had 7 so this how it worked;
Input #***ABCDEFGH-595B * 
it has to be in caps or it wont work.
I had found the dell.exe elsewhere on the web but it is the exact same thing I used.
